rows.label: qst105605_msg001
rows.name: 俺はここで反乱分子を食い止める

rows.label: qst105605_msg101
rows.name: 目的は達成できた？ 何のことだ？

rows.label: qst105605_msg0001
rows.name:
We'll take care of here! Your
Highness should search the castle
and subdue any remaining opposition!

rows.label: qst105605_msg0101
rows.name:
Leave the insurgents to us!
Take care, Your Highness!

rows.label: qst105605_msg0102
rows.name:
I would say we've succeeded, but
I'd rather not speak too soon...
